certainty in the magnetic field\ninference prevents a sufficiently accurate determination of the spatial\nderivatives. We present a method that allows the inference of the three\ncomponents of the electric current vector at deep atmospheric layers\n(photospheric layers) from spectropolarimetric observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Dec 2021 16:08:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-22"}
