te that hierarchy sensitivity of optimized P2O does not\nget significantly better than DUNE for the current favourable values of\n$\\delta_{\\rm CP}$ which is $180^\\circ < \\delta_{\\rm CP} < 360^\\circ$ as\nobtained by the global analysis in both standard three flavour and in presence\nof NSI.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Dec 2021 13:03:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Apr 2022 11:59:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-08"}
